)$ work. As a consequence, it also improves the\nstate-of-the-art sequential running time from $m\\cdot 2^{O(\\sqrt{\\log n})}$ to\n$m\\mathrm{poly}(\\log n)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2019 17:33:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-06"}
