d SC-P-based BICM-ID systems can achieve even better error performance\nwith the aid of the VNMM scheme. As a consequence, the proposed LBPM\nconstellation mappers and VNMM scheme make the SC-P-based BICM-ID systems a\nfavorable choice for the future-generation wireless communication systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Nov 2019 07:14:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-07"}
